vote.title:
A public hearing to receive comments regarding an application for and an ordinance granting an amendment to Planned Development District No. 994 on property bounded by South Lancaster Road, Ann Arbor Avenue, South Denley Drive, and Paducah Avenue
Recommendation of Staff:  Approval, subject to an amended development plan, an amended landscape plan, an amended traffic management plan, and amended conditions
Recommendation of CPC:  Approval, subject to an amended development plan, an amended landscape plan, an amended traffic management plan, and amended conditions
Z223-293(DM)
